<br>
I'm a level 7 MA and have noticed that at the rate I am going I will need to get more NCUs.  I keep toughen skin up, iron fist, and controled rage at all times taking 3 of 8.  I'm guessing that by around 15 or so I'll be out.  Maybe I'm thinking too far ahead, but how do I get more NCUs?  What skills will I need to bump up?  Where do I get them?<br>
<br>
Also, should I be worrying about implats at this time?<br>
<br>
Adapa<br>
